{"name": "odoo12-addon-base-location", "metadata": {"name": "odoo12-addon-base-location", "version": "12.0.1.1.4", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 12.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/partner-contact", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Enhanced zip/npa management system", "upload_time": 1637585506}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fpartner--contact-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/partner-contact\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/partner-contact/tree/12.0/base_location\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/partner-contact-12-0/partner-contact-12-0-base_location\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runbot-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runbot\n    :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/134/12.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Location management (aka Better ZIP)\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module introduces a zip model that allows you to manage locations in a better way.\n\nThe zips will allow the users to complete automatically all address-related fields by just filling the zip.\n\nAlso allows different search filters.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\n1. Go to *Contacts / Configuration / Localization / Cities*.\n2. Create a new City.\n3. Go to *Contacts / Configuration / Localization / Zips*.\n4. Create a new Zip and relate it to the city (you can also create the Zip from the City).\n\nor, with module 'Contacts Directory' installed:\n#. Go to *Contacts / Configuration / Localization / Countries*.\n#. Locate the desired country.\n#. Press on the button 'Cities' / 'Zips'.\n\n## Usage\n\n1. Access a partner record\n2. Fill the field *Location completion*\n3. Information about country, state, city and zip will be filled automatically\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/partner-contact/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/partner-contact/issues/new?body=module:%20base_location%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n- ACYSOS S.L.\n- Alejandro Santana\n- Tecnativa\n- AdaptiveCity\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Nicolas Bessi (Camptocamp)\n- Ignacio Ibeas (Acysos S.L.)\n- Pedro M. Baeza \\<<mailto:pedro.baeza@gmail.com>>\n- Alejandro Santana \\<<mailto:alejandrosantana@anubia.es>>\n- Sandy Carter \\<<mailto:sandy.carter@savoirfairelinux.com>>\n- Yannick Vaucher \\<<mailto:yannick.vaucher@camptocamp.com>>\n- Francesco Apruzzese \\<<mailto:f.apruzzese@apuliasoftware.it>>\n- Dave Lasley \\<<mailto:dave@laslabs.com>>\n- Aitor Bouzas \\<<mailto:aitor.bouzas@adaptivecity.com>>\n\n### Other credits\n\n- Icon park: `Icon http://icon-park.com/icon/location-map-pin-orange3/`\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/partner-contact](https://github.com/OCA/partner-contact/tree/12.0/base_location) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models.res_city", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.base_location.models..res_city", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models.res_city_zip", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.base_location.models..res_city_zip", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models.res_company", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.base_location.models..res_company", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models.res_partner", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.base_location.models..res_partner", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models.res_city", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 Aitor Bouzas <aitor.bouzas@adaptivecity.com>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models.res_city.City", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models.res_city.City._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.base_location.models.res_city.Ci